Privacy Policy for NoPhoneNoEmail
Effective Date: 7/19/2025
1. Introduction
No Phone NoEmail ("we", "us", or "our") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you use the NoPhoneNoEmail mobile application ("App").
2. Information We Collect
a. No Personal Contact Information Required
NoPhoneNoEmail does not require you to provide your phone number, email address, or any personal contact information to use the app.
b. User-Generated Content
Messages you send and receive
Photos and files you share
Audio messages you record
Username/display name (if you choose to set one)
c. Device Information
Device model and operating system version
App usage statistics for performance improvement
Push notification tokens for message delivery
Anonymized device identifier
d. Optional Features
Geolocation data (only if you grant permission and enable location sharing)
3. How We Use Your Information
To provide secure messaging services
To deliver messages to intended recipients
To improve app performance and user experience
To ensure the security and integrity of the app
To send push notifications for new messages
To comply with legal obligations
4. Data Sharing and Disclosure
We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties
Your messages and content are encrypted and only accessible to you and your intended recipients
We may disclose information if required by law or to protect our rights and users' safety
5. Data Security
All messages are encrypted end-to-end using industry-standard encryption
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your data
All data is transmitted over encrypted connections
Messages are stored temporarily for delivery and then deleted
6. Children's Privacy
NoPhoneNoEmail is not intended for children under the age of 13
We do not knowingly collect personal information from children
7. Your Choices
You may choose not to use the app if you do not agree with this policy
You can delete your account and all associated data at any time
You can request deletion of your data by contacting us at [info@ilighttech.com]
8. Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time
Changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date
9. Contact Us
If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy or your data, please contact us at:
Email: [info@ilighttech.com]
Company: iLight Tech LLC
